quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  10,21,"Si Men mee…óinirii sirkoo…ìe …ìen neema to…ìo e amo …ìaawo nde hokkere e …ìi…ótteende he…ìi…ìe, jaka yoo hi…ìe jalkita fenna Aayeeje Amen …óen. An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìenn sirkoo…ìe : "Ko Alla …ìuri yaccaade fewjoore, …ìuri yaawude kadi nanngugol on lepta". Pellet, Malaa'ikaa…ìe winndoo…ìe …ìen hino winndude ko fewjoton kon, huunde e munlaawa- taako …ìe, ko honno …óum laaworta tagu…óo …ìe on? Alla yo…ìitoyay on e pewje mon …óen."
  10,22,"Ko Alla woni On doginoowo on, onon …ìee yim…ìe, ka njorndi, e hoore koy…óe mon maa e hoore daabeeji mon. Ko kanko kadi woni doginoowo on ka maayo e nder laa…óe mon. Haa si on wonii ka laa…óe maayo, …óe doginira …ìe henndu laa…ìundu, wa…ó…óii…ìe …ìen weltora ndun henndu laa…ìundu. E nder nden weltaare ma…ì…ìe, hanndu nduluuru (duleendu bippooru ara e ma…ì…ìe, molloode molloo…óe(bempejje) ara e ma…ì…ìe iwrabanngeeji …ói fow, …ìe fellita wonnde kam…ìe …ìe halkoto woni, ontuma …ìe toroo Alla tun, …ìe kafidataa Mo e go…ó…óum goo, …ìe wi'a :"Si tawii tun A da…óndii men e …óee jaribaaji …óoo, pellet, men laatodat e yettoo…ìe Ma …ìe e dow ko neemin…óaa kon e amen"."
  10,23,"Nde Alla jaabinoo …ìe toraare ma…ì…ìe nden, O da…ó- ndi…ìe …óen ta∆¥aale, e jaka yoo kam…ìe hi…ìe bonnira ka leydi faggitagol keeferaaku, e geddi e bakkaatu. Finee faamon, onon …ìee yim…ìe, wonnde battane bewre mon bonnde nden, ko e hoore mon yantata. Bewre mon lorrataa Alla. ∆äum ko ko dakmitoron e …óam nguurndam aduna lannoo-jam, refti ko ka Amen woni ruttorde mon √ëalnde Darngal, Men yeetitoo on ko gerayno…óon e geddi, Men yo…ìita on …óum."
  10,24,"Anndee misal aduna nguurndam aduna …óam …óam dakmitorton ko lannata he√±a, ko wano to…ìo jillondiroowo e pu…ói leydi ndin, gabbe e dim…óe e hu…óo ko yim…ìe e neemoraa…ói √±aamata. Haa si leydi ndin ∆¥ettii mbaadi mun njal…ìundi ndin, ndi labinorii ko ndi fu…óini kon e nooji pu…ói, yim…ìe mayri ndin jikka wonnde ko …ìe hattam…ìe so√±ugol tetta ko ndi fu…óini kon, √±aawoore Amen halko …óum ara e mayri, Men wa…ótina ndi so√±iraandi wa si tawnii ndi …óuu…óiraani le…ó…óe e pu…ói ado mun. Ko wano no Men …ìannginirani on fiyaaku aduna on e yaawugol lannugol makko, Men …ìannginirta …ìanngannduyeeji e hujjaaji …ìen miijitoo…ìe taskoo."
  10,25,"Alla nodda yim…ìe …ìen denndaangal faade Aljanna Makko on, on woni galle kisal (daaru salaam). Ko …óon yim…ìe …ìen hisata e masiboo e annde, …ìe hisa kadi e maayde. Alla no fewnira on Mo o muuyi e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen faade e diina lisalaamu hewtinayka e galle kisal …óen."